title: Exploratory Data Analysis
description: This was an analysis of zoning data in different municipalities in Massachusetts, exploring how different exclusionary zoning policies affected types of homes constructed.

title: Visualization Design
description: This was an analysis of population data from the US Census, looking at how population counts across different genders have changed over the past century.

title: Bikewatching
description: This was a visualization of some Massachusetts bike line and station activity over time, seen on a map of Cambridge and Boston.

title: Persuasive or Deceptive Visualization?
description: This was an exploration of how different visualizations can warp and twist what readers perceive through seemingly simple or innocuous design decisions; it explored the boundaries between ethical and honest visualization.
